get.description:
### API Request Description

This endpoint makes an HTTP GET request to retrieve a list of pending items.

### API Response

The response is a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
    "datos": [
        {
            "codigo": 0,
            "creado": 0,
            "modificado": 0,
            "modulo": "",
            "accion": "",
            "idProceso": 0,
            "mensaje": "",
            "link": {
                "url": "",
                "tipo": "",
                "metadata": {
                    "version": "",
                    "timestamp": 0
                },
                "rutaBase": "",
                "parametros": {
                    "ver": "",
                    "accion": "",
                    "codigo": 0,
                    "categoria": ""
                }
            }
        }
    ],
    "success": true,
    "cantidad": 0
}

 ```

